Chordate:


Chordate sighed, watching Feline's heavenly figure, looking at all her 
curves.  Her walk was almost celestial to Chordate.  He walked over to her 
after she had asked him to join her, sitting down next to her, taking a big 
gulp of his liquid energon, looking at her tail, then looking over her 
beautiful face.
"So...where'd you come from?"
